1. *Onom* je lako pronaći rešenje. (It is easy to find a solution for him.)
2. On je predložio *onom* da se zaposli. (He suggested to him to get employed.)
3. Svi smo se složili sa *onom*. (We all agreed with him.)
4. *Onom* je bilo teško da se odluči. (It was difficult for him to decide.)
5. *Onom* su pomogli da pronađe posao. (They helped him to find a job.)